subject: Basketball
College Athletics
NCAA Basketball Tournament (Men)
lead_paragraph: UConn’s Hasheem Thabeet had only six rebounds in 36 minutes, well below his season average of 10.9. He was 6 of 13 from the field and made 5 of 7 free throws.
